BOScoin (BOS) Logo BOScoin (BOS) platform consistently refer to it as “the Self-Evolving Cryptocurrency Platform”. BOScoin was developed on two core constructs, referred to as Trust Contracts and The Congress Network. Trust Contracts act as a framework for the creation of executable contracts on the blockchain, whereas The Congress Network refers to the mechanism aiming to create more democratic and productive decision making. Source
